metadata.Summary: This frame shows the configuration panel for the 'Google Gemini Chat Model' node within n8n. The 'Parameters' tab is active, and the user is prompted to connect this node to an AI Chain. The model is set to 'models/gemini-2.0-flash', and the credential is set to 'Google Gemini(PaLM) Api account'. The 'Wire me up' help box is visible, guiding the user on how to connect the node within the workflow.
metadata.ActionsDetected: Configuring Google Gemini Chat Model node, Setting node parameters, Attempting to connect node in workflow, Following 'Wire me up' guidance
